description:
[English]
Hello, fellow tenno, here comes another wonderful day and month of the seasons, when everyone will fill with happiness and peace in their heart, what? You mean you didn’t? that’s why we are here ,dear : )

Resently we just started another brand new journey on Venus , which can allow us to skate like sonic the hedgehog on the snowy land so I’m thinking it will be a (insert Link meme here: )”Great” idea, for combining this gameplay with wonderful holiday spirit , and with more dank meme which you like it a lot :p

So enjoy it, and may the snow shines bright and the jingle belling everywhere you go, and don’t forget to leave a comment and like below since this is my very first warframe video 

Let’s ride like a wind ,shall we?

Sean&Macaron
(by the way, I changed my sign resently, reason you can see on my DeviantArt here, I change my avater-oc’s setting now :
https://www.deviantart.com/avchonline/art/BoV-announcement-two-is-batter-than-one-775716320
)

=======================================
[中文]
各位親愛的田螺們早灣，又來到那一年中最美麗的季節，因為我們要給你們心中填滿歡喜與平安，蝦米？你說你沒感覺？不然你以為我們是來做什麼的好朋友？: )
最近金星才剛開啟了嶄新的旅程，金星平原上的全新體驗，包括騎著滑板像音速小子般奔馳於冰天雪地中這給了我一個點子，讓這個季節的歡笑結合這活動呈現給大家，還不少迷因(meme)搏君一笑

這是我第一支warframe影片，並祝福大家內心的聖誕鈴聲不停歇，也感謝您在這影片下留言與喜歡，我們下次見
並且要在這裡深深感謝氏族團長shinchenwucheng與氏族成員paradise-black的參與，使這影片更加的美好，這裡奉獻上我的感謝

親王&馬卡龍
